sql:
SELECT 
    C_YEAR,
    C_MONTH,
    QC_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT QC_NAME) AS "岸桥数",
    SUM(L_D_S_MOVE) AS "装卸船作业量_钩",
    SUM(L_D_S_UNIT) AS "装卸船作业量_Unit",
    SUM(L_D_S_TEU) AS "装卸船作业量_TEU",
    SUM(HATCHCOVER_HOOK) AS "舱盖板作业量",
    SUM(SHOB_HOOK) AS "翻箱作业量",
    SUM(OTHER_HOOK) AS "其他作业量",
    ROUND(SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / 3600.00, 2) AS "总作业小时_h",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN ROUND(SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / 3600.00, 2) > 0 
            THEN SUM(L_D_S_MOVE) / ROUND(SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / 3600.00, 2) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "总效率_钩_h",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN ROUND(SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / 3600.00, 2) > 0 
            THEN SUM(L_D_S_UNIT) / ROUND(SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / 3600.00, 2) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "总效率_unit_h",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN ROUND(SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / 3600.00, 2) > 0 
            THEN SUM(L_D_S_TEU) / ROUND(SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / 3600.00, 2) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "总效率_TEU_h",
    MAX(L_D_CYCLE_DURATION) AS "最大循环时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(L_D_S_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(CYCLE_DURATION) / SUM(L_D_S_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "平均循环时长_s",
    MIN(L_D_CYCLE_DURATION) AS "最小循环时长_s",
    MAX(L_D_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "最大海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(L_D_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(L_D_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) / SUM(L_D_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "平均海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MIN(L_D_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "最小海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MAX(L_D_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "最大陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(L_D_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(L_D_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) / SUM(L_D_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "平均陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MIN(L_D_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "最小陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    SUM(LOAD_S_MOVE) AS "装船作业量_钩",
    SUM(LOAD_S_UNIT) AS "装船作业量_Unit",
    SUM(LOAD_S_TEU) AS "装船作业量_TEU",
    MAX(LOAD_CYCLE_DURATION) AS "装船最大循环时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(LOAD_S_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(LOAD_CYCLE_DURATION) / SUM(LOAD_S_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "装船平均循环时长_s",
    MIN(LOAD_CYCLE_DURATION) AS "装船最小循环时长_s",
    MAX(LOAD_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "装船最大海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(LOAD_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(LOAD_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) / SUM(LOAD_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "装船平均海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MIN(LOAD_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "装船最小海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MAX(LOAD_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "装船最大陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(LOAD_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(LOAD_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) / SUM(LOAD_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "装船平均陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MIN(LOAD_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "装船最小陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    SUM(DSCH_S_MOVE) AS "卸船作业量_钩",
    SUM(DSCH_S_UNIT) AS "卸船作业量_Unit",
    SUM(DSCH_S_TEU) AS "卸船作业量_TEU",
    MAX(DSCH_CYCLE_DURATION) AS "卸船最大循环时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(DSCH_S_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(DSCH_CYCLE_DURATION) / SUM(DSCH_S_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "卸船平均循环时长_s",
    MIN(DSCH_CYCLE_DURATION) AS "卸船最小循环时长_s",
    MAX(DSCH_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "卸船最大海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(DSCH_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(DSCH_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) / SUM(DSCH_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "卸船平均海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MIN(DSCH_WS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "卸船最小海侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MAX(DSCH_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "卸船最大陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    ROUND(
        CASE 
            WHEN SUM(DSCH_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) > 0 
            THEN SUM(DSCH_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) / SUM(DSCH_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_MOVE) 
            ELSE 0 
        END, 2
    ) AS "卸船平均陆侧安全高度以下时长_s",
    MIN(DSCH_LS_HST_UNDER_SH_DURATION) AS "卸船最小陆侧安全高度以下时长_s"
FROM 
    V_DWM_QC_MT_CYCLE
WHERE 
    C_YEAR = '2025'
    AND C_MONTH = '05'
    AND QC_NAME = '105'
GROUP BY 
    C_YEAR, C_MONTH, QC_NAME
ORDER BY 
    C_YEAR, C_MONTH, QC_NAME;

summary: 2025年5月，岸桥105#共作业232.41小时，完成装卸船作业量4149 TEU，总效率为17.85 TEU/小时。其中装船2266 TEU、卸船1883 TEU，卸船平均循环时长（493.1秒）高于装船（285.08秒），作业效率存在优化空间。舱盖板、翻箱等辅助作业较少，主作业占比高。海侧与陆侧安全高度以下时长数据缺失，建议加强设备运行细节监控以进一步提升作业效能。
